OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and bright with a light
OL,6,Fbreeze. Long periods of hazy sunshine.
OL,7,FAnother hot day, though perhaps a
OL,8,Flittle cooler near the coast where a
OL,9,Fsea breeze develops.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FPerhaps a little more cloud
OL,12,Fnear the Kent coast but long clear
OL,13,Fspells are expected elsewhere. Light
OL,14,Fwinds allowing the odd mist patch to
OL,15,Fform.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FVariable amounts of cloud
OL,18,Fthrough the morning but turning
OL,19,Fbrighter by lunchtime, especially
OL,20,Ffurther south and west where it will
OL,21,Fbe hot. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
