OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fand sunny to end the week. Light winds
OL,7,Fon Thursday, though breezier on Friday
OL,8,Fand Saturday. Hot throughout with
OL,9,Ftropical nights likely, especially in
OL,10,Furban areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
